juniDvmrpAgentV1.name: juniDvmrpAgentV1
juniDvmrpAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the DVMRP component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the DVMRP component was supported in JUNOSe 3.0 thru 4.x
        system releases.
juniDvmrpAgentV1.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DVMRP application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when new objects were added to the Juniper-DVMRP-MIB.

juniDvmrpAgentV2.name: juniDvmrpAgentV2
juniDvmrpAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the DVMRP component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the DVMRP component is supported in JUNOSe 5.0 and subsequent
        system releases.
juniDvmrpAgentV2.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the DVMRP application in JUNOSe.
